time complexity: O(N)
space complexity: O(1)
energy implications: LOW
explanation: The solution iterates over the string once, storing the first occurrence of each character. It then updates the maximum length between equal characters. The space complexity is considered O(1) because the number of unique lowercase English letters is constant (26), making the space usage constant.

